content.text:
I'm ready to help you with your Domain-Driven Design architecture repository. I can see you have several uncommitted changes including:

- Modified Claude settings
- Changes to architecture definitions (Flybuys integration, Salesforce customer support)
- Navigation file updates
- A new initiatives directory
- Deleted executive summaries and a conversion script

How can I assist you today? I can help with:

- Committing these changes with appropriate commit messages
- Working with Context Mapper (CML) files and their paired markdown documentation
- Generating diagrams from CML files
- Reviewing bounded context definitions
- Or any other architecture-related tasks

What would you like to work on?
